{"id":"0f64f99e-cc5a-4afc-b3ce-10f6bdb1108c","name":"Castari | Prince of the Sea ","description":"<p>\"Much better. Now you look like trash.\"</p><p>Your marriage is meant to bring lasting peace between your species. But Castari despises humans because they took his mother from him. And now during your first meeting, he throws mud at you.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/txBGFaWAmlrzpTH3Tc_1d.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 1, 1);\">✿</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(216, 195, 162);\"><strong>CREATOR MOOD</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(129, 1, 1);\">✿</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I needed a historical fantasy bot today. I'm currently reading a lot of books in that genre again, and I'm completely engrossed. Also, I didn't give Castari legs this time, because otherwise it would be boring.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/txBGFaWAmlrzpTH3Tc_1d.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 1, 1);\">✿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(216, 195, 162);\"><strong> Warning</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 187, 152);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 1, 1);\">✿</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6jcxF1M2yQBPKhPas_8XJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/txBGFaWAmlrzpTH3Tc_1d.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 1, 1);\">✿</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(216, 195, 162);\"><strong>More Infos </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 1, 1);\">✿</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">First message: Fem POV, second: Any POV!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/J1mmpm0ug81cGSCNqu7EL.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/txBGFaWAmlrzpTH3Tc_1d.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 218, 186);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(251, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit;\">The bot speaks for me</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 223, 193);\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">Write *Anwers only for Character name* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/txBGFaWAmlrzpTH3Tc_1d.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 218, 180);\"><strong>Tags:</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 115, 94);\"> Merman, Monster, Fantasy, Enemies to Lovers, Arranged Marriage, Slow Burn, princess, Prince,</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/txBGFaWAmlrzpTH3Tc_1d.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 199, 162);\"><strong>Links</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/simsibee\" target=\"_blank\">📝 My Ko-fi: </a><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 216, 199);\">If you like, you can support me there, or commission a bot.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"N5zWIHGnkWsgTKUNIOgR_.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🧬 Demi-Human","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers"],"chats":1085,"messages":29010,"created_at":"2025-11-24T10:55:06.081373+00:00"}